[Phuket is located in southern Thailand on the Strait of Malacca and
can be found on a map of the country at:
<http://www.un.org/Depts/Cartographic/map/profile/thailand.pdf>. The
area was extensively affected by the tsunami on 26 Dec 2004. - Mod.LL]
